336
00:24:04,880 --> 00:24:08,670
Two more people got carried away. A total of five people have died now.

337
00:24:11,130 --> 00:24:13,530
Call all the physicians together tonight. We'll quicken our pace in testing the prescriptions.

338
00:24:13,530 --> 00:24:16,010
We must find the cure to the pox as soon as possible.

339
00:24:16,010 --> 00:24:18,340
Is this medicine to save people or poison

340
00:24:18,340 --> 00:24:21,480
- that kills people?
