341
00:24:21,480 --> 00:24:22,870
I'm sorry.

342
00:24:22,870 --> 00:24:25,520
We all know about what happened last night.

343
00:24:25,520 --> 00:24:28,310
Today, corpses were carried out

344
00:24:28,310 --> 00:24:30,240
