345
00:24:30,240 --> 00:24:32,950
- Will it be our turn soon?
- Older Sister! Older Sister!

346
00:24:32,950 --> 00:24:36,080
Calm down. Calm down.

347
00:24:36,080 --> 00:24:38,380
Stop lying to us.

348
