490
00:33:05,400 --> 00:33:10,100
She said that "those who've mastered medicine save people.

491
00:33:10,100 --> 00:33:14,800
Those who've mastered medical ethics save the world." She chose the latter.

492
00:33:18,700 --> 00:33:21,200
If everyone truly does not want to stay to treat this illness,

493
00:33:21,200 --> 00:33:24,800
